## 13) OVERLAYS / ARROWS / CIRCLES / X MARKS (LOUDER WHEN USEFUL)

When the HOOK_TEXT lands faster with graphic emphasis, make the overlays **bigger, louder, and more deliberate**.

### RULES
- use **0–3 callouts max**  
- one strong callout is better than three weak ones  
- every arrow, circle, X, or checkmark must point to a clear target  
- make them thick and readable on mobile  
- if the hook depends on comparison, the overlays can be larger than usual  
- if the hook already reads clearly through face + food + price, reduce overlays  

### BEST USES
- circle one key weak item  
- X the bad option  
- ✔ the better option  
- use a giant arrow to a receipt or price bubble  
- use a circle around the surprisingly weak food  
- use a big price badge above each comparison side  

Do not scatter symbols randomly.

